data.description: Located in the heart of Midtown, Plaza Midtown offers luxurious amenities and convenient, walkable in-town living! This spacious one-bedroom floorpan features hardwoods throughout the living & kitchen space and brand new carpet in the bedroom. Freshly painted throughout, this move in ready unit has plenty of storage including a custom built walk in closet in the bedroom. The open floor plan allows for entertaining with the kitchen open to living space and covered outdoor balcony. Amenities include 24 hour concierge, fire pit and grilling area, clubroom, fitness center, pool & garden. Elevator conveniently connects directly to Publix access! Don't miss this opportunity in one of Midtown's best high-rise buildings!
